        "voice_id": "en_narrator",
        "text": "Maya hesitated, then approached. 'Clara? Is that really you?' she asked, her voice barely audible over the rain. Clara looked up, her eyes widening in surprise. 'Maya! I can't believe it,' she exclaimed, standing up.",
