      {
        "segment_id": "s4",
        "speaker_id": "narrator",
        "voice_id": "en_narrator",
        "text": "They stood for a few minutes, catching up on the years that had passed. Clara mentioned she was moving back to the city for a new job and suggested they meet for coffee the following day. 'I'd love to,' Maya agreed, feeling a warmth spread through her despite the cold.",
